    Scope and Contents
The file consists of announcements, agendas, memoranda, and reports. Announcement topic regarding Dr. Lorman Ratner'a visit to SSU to make recommendations regarding faculty governance.  Agenda topics include Dr. Ratner's visit, tenure policy and evaluation of SSU President Lacy.  Memoranda are from committee mebers to Faculty Senate, Vice President for Academic Affairs, Cullom Davis and the university community.  Reports nclude academic program review statements and Senate Committee appointments.  
  
